Package: WofostR
Type: Package
Title: R Implementation of Wofost Crop Growth Algorithm
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Luca Butikofer
Maintainer: Luca Butikofer <lucabutikofer@gmail.com>
Description: Implements Wofost Crop Growth Algorithm for potential production
             and its independent subroutines Astro, Assimilation,
             CH2O conversion and partitioning, Roots, Leaf and Storage organs
             dynamics. Water-limited production is implemented via hydrotools
             package. Automatic sourcing of high-res weather data via
             microclima package. Crop suitability functions provided too.
License: EUPL (>= 1.1)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Imports: yaml(>= 2.2.0.9999), methods, httr
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Remotes: viking/r-yaml
